rows.label: tev078501_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Conichien about the tyrants in Primordia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Conichien about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Conichien about the tyrants in Primordia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0001
rows.name:
The one they call Yelena, the Sequestered,
has been sighted on the East Janpath Plain.
*fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0002
rows.name:
I hear she's not easy to find, but if you search the
areas where scirpos flock, you might get lucky. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0003
rows.name:
Incidentally, I've heard that scirpo abdomens hold some
truly high-quality voltant. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0004
rows.name:
I couldn't tell you if that's actually true or not. *fsssh*
But if you ever manage to crack one open,
come back and tell me how it went![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0008
rows.name:
I'd like to collect all the Miralife Cards depicting
venomous indigens. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0009
rows.name:
But I don't have any money left to pay for cards!
I wonder how I can make some around here? *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0010
rows.name:
...What? *fsssh* You say I could join BLADE and accept
jobs from Mission Control?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0011
rows.name:
I certainly share BLADE's interest in indigens, but...
Well, if I were to leave this city, I doubt I could survive
even a single hit from such a monster. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0012
rows.name:
There has to be a safer way to make money that still
involves dealing with venomous beasts. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0020
rows.name:
I've heard of a species of indigen known as adsecula
that favors the damp of the Silent Mire. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0021
rows.name:
Apparently one of them is a real tough customer that's
already fought off a number of BLADEs. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0022
rows.name:
Heh heh. *fsssh* As a bit of a basement dweller myself,
I can't help but take a little pride in that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0023
rows.name:
Um...b-but of course I take no pleasure in the defeat of
our noble BLADEs. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Conichien about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0013
rows.name:
I spend most of my day staring at those cards you
gave me. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0014
rows.name:
I want more of them! But I don't have any money,
so there's not much I can do. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev078501_MSG0015
rows.name:
I guess I'll have to gather up more unusual bones and
grasses to trade to collectors. *fsssh*[ST:wait ]
